2013年，[[史蒂夫·巴爾默|史蒂夫·巴爾默]]宣布微軟公司部門重整計畫，將微軟分割為四大事業集團，茱莉·拉森葛林升任微軟副總裁，主管設備與工作室工程集團（Devices and Studios Engineering Group），負責監督所有硬體，包括平板電腦[[Surface|Surface]]、電玩主機[[Xbox|Xbox]]和相關遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-12/bodyslams-at-microsoft-prepared-larson-green-for-overhaul.html |title=Bass, Dina. "Bodyslams at Microsoft Prepared Larson-Green for Overhaul" ''[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]]'' July 12, 2013 |access-date=2015-08-13 |archive-date=2014-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304113222/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-12/bodyslams-at-microsoft-prepared-larson-green-for-overhaul.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 然而一些歧视女性的遊戲玩家对这个消息十分失望<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/technology/2013/07/gamers-cant-handle-new-female-head-xbox/67073/ |title=Greenfield, Rebecca. "Gamers Can't Handle the New Female Head at Xbox" ''[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] Wire'', July 11, 2013 |access-date=2015-08-13 |archive-date=2013-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928055026/http://www.theatlanticwire.com/technology/2013/07/gamers-cant-handle-new-female-head-xbox/67073/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2013/07/24/julie-larson-green-and-the-misogyny-of-gaming.html | title=Game On: A Woman Takes the Helm of X-Box.  Misogyny ensues. | work=[[Daily_Beast|Daily Beast]] | date=24 July 2013 | accessdate=28 July 2013 | author=Ross, Winston | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922161517/http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2013/07/24/julie-larson-green-and-the-misogyny-of-gaming.html | archive-date=2013-09-22 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailydot.com/lifestyle/sexist-gamers-microsoft-xbox-julie-larson-green/ | title=Sexist gamers can't stand that a woman now heads Xbox | work=[[The_Daily_Dot|The Daily Dot]] | date=12 July 2013 | accessdate=28 July 2013 | author=Sampson, Ted | archive-date=2016-04-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web